"the web, &lt;<ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/spectacle\">https://apps.kde."
"org/spectacle</ulink>&gt;"
msgstr ""
"IRC इत्यत्र, irc.libera.chat #kde इत्यत्र अथवा ईमेलद्वारा, kde-graphics-devel@kde."
"org इत्यत्र अथवा जालपुटे, &lt;<ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/spectacle"
"\">https: //apps.kde.org/तमाशा</ulink>&gt;"

